A warmly lit convention hall scene in Studio Ghibli style, showing a diverse crowd of animated characters in yellow clothing gathered in small clusters, engaged in animated conversation and laughter. The space has a magical quality with soft golden light filtering through large windows, casting long afternoon shadows. In the foreground, several figures exchange ideas with expressive gestures, their faces showing genuine delight and connection. Scattered throughout are whimsical details: steaming cups of coffee floating on small tables, colorful conference badges hanging from lanyards, and a gentle sense of movement as people drift between groups. The color palette emphasizes warm yellows, soft oranges, and creamy whites, with the characteristic soft brushwork and dreamlike atmosphere of Japanese animation. The scene conveys the energy of meaningful human connections being forged at a gathering of passionate enthusiasts.
